      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "<p>Fill in the missing reagents <b>a</b>–<b>d</b> in the following synthesis of racemic methamphetamine from benzene.</p>\n<img src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBblFhIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--d2628b552a652e3a4b11e6d4ac1bf3c6295928a9/OChem_24_EC_048.jpg\" alt=\"Benzene reacts with a to produce allylbenzene. This reacts with b and c to produce 1-phenylpropan-2-one. This reacts with d to form (R, S)-methamphetamine.\">",
